joinSets

public void joinSets(FeatureHolderStyleToken token,
                     FeatureFilter featureFilter)
Performs a AND operation of the feature filter of the first set with the provided feature filter. That is, (NEW FILTER) = new FeatureFilter.And((OLD SET FILTER), (PROVIDED FILTER))

Parameters:
token - The original set.
featureFilter - The feature filter to append / join.
